{"tid":1850772,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"網傳沙田盜竊案 打爆私家車玻璃偷6盒口罩","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T07:43:44.000Z","uid":5195,"like":219,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"ec064492e194f8273db8714ebe34c2e914962ac0","tid":1850772,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKrs20J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKrs20J.jpg&h=488c0548&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ed0cc7834707b8b9ae954723626bb0bf092aee5","tid":1850772,"uid":258731,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔"},{"pid":"4d8743b1553c854dcb1aaf8849bc4e3e5bee23c